form(ng-submit="ok()")
  .modal-header
    h3 Import
  .modal-body
    .form-group
      label(for="importtype") From
      select.form-control(id="importtype",ng-model="importtype",ng-options="type.name for type in importtypes",required)
    p(ng-if="importtype.name == 'dsbudget'").
      Please upload your dsBudget document (BudgetDocument.xml) stored on your computer to import data.  
      If you are not sure how to find it, please contact dsBudget support forum.</p>
    .form-group
      label(for="fd") Currency Fraction Digits 
      p.
        Please select number of digits under major denomination in your currrency. 
        For example, for USD(like $.00), it is 2 and for JPY(&yen;) it is 0.
      input(type="text" ng-model="fd" required).form-control

    .form-group
      label(for="importfile") Data File
      input#importfile(type="file" ng-file-select="onFileSelect($files)" required)

    div(ng-show="showprogress")
      {{progress_action}} ...
      progressbar(value="progress").progress-striped.active {{progress}}%

    div.modal-footer
      button(type="submit" ng-disabled="showprogress").btn.btn-primary Import
      button(type="button" ng-click="cancel()").btn.btn-default Cancel

